# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GameHub — Environment Variables
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env.local for local overrides.
# Variables prefixed with VITE_ are bundled into the client build.
# DO NOT commit .env.local or .env.production to source control.
#
# ── No environment variables are required for the default Vercel setup ──
#
# The CORS proxy for GameMonetize and HTMLGames is handled by Vercel Edge
# Functions in api/gm/[...path].js and api/hg/[...path].js, which are
# deployed automatically alongside the app. No extra configuration needed.
#
# ── Optional: Cloudflare Worker alternative ──────────────────────────────
# If you deploy to a platform other than Vercel (e.g. Netlify, GitHub Pages,
# a static CDN), you can use the Cloudflare Worker in workers/cors-proxy/
# as the proxy instead. In that case:
#
#   1. Deploy the worker:  npx wrangler deploy
#   2. Set this variable to the printed worker URL
#   3. Re-enable the _PROXY branching logic in src/services/gameApi.js
#
# VITE_CORS_PROXY_URL=https://gamehub-cors-proxy.YOUR-SUBDOMAIN.workers.dev
